snippet.title: Stormgate Developer Update
snippet.description:
Stormgate is an upcoming free-to-play real-time strategy game developed by Frost Giant Studios. 

- Learn more and sign up for the beta at https://playstormgate.com/
- Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2012510/
- Subscribe to the newsletter: https://frostgiant.com/#subscribe.
